										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>More details have been released for the <a href="https://vocadb.net/Ar/1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hatsune Miku</a> Noodle Stopper Figure by <a href="https://www.furyu.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Furyu</a>! Read on for a closer look at this cute prize figure and for details of the release date and where to find it.</p>
<h2>Product Details</h2>
<p>This figure is made with PVC, is approximately 14 cm tall, weighs approximately 300 grams, and shall be available from 20th September.</p>
<p>The adorable Miku figure features Miku sitting in a relaxed pose. The idea is to use her as a &#8216;noodle stopper&#8217; to sit on top of a noodle cup while you&#8217;re waiting for the them to soak up the water, as you can see below.</p>
<figure id="attachment_242298" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-242298" style="width: 300px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Usage-Example.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img class="wp-image-242298 size-medium" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Usage-Example-300x300.jpg" alt="Miku Noodle Stopper Usage Example" width="300" height="300" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Usage-Example-300x300.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Usage-Example-150x150.jpg 150w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Usage-Example-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Usage-Example-800x800.jpg 800w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Usage-Example-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><figcaption id="caption-attachment-242298" class="wp-caption-text">Example of Usage as a Noodle Stopper</figcaption></figure>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>However, you can place Miku on top of any flat surface, shown below.</p>
<p>A close inspection shows that you can see the figure features various small details, such as Miku&#8217;s 02 marking on her shoulder, the lights, and buttons on her skirt.</p>
<p>One of my favourite details is her hair flowing and curling behind her, which seems to resemble the curly noodles that Miku would keep watch over for you.</p>

