<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Artwork</h2>
<p>Here are a few images of the final artwork that the figure is based on as well as a couple of rough sketches done by the artist, <a href="https://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=178217" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Kuroboshii Kohaku</a>.</p>
<p>It&#8217;s amazing to see how this lovely artwork has come to life as a fun and functional prize figure.</p>

<a href='/more-details-on-the-miku-noodle-stopper-figure-by-furyu/miku-noodle-stopper-artwork/'><img width="150" height="150" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Artwork-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail" alt="Miku Noodle Stopper Artwork" loading="lazy" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Artwork-150x150.jpg 150w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Artwork-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /></a>
<a href='/more-details-on-the-miku-noodle-stopper-figure-by-furyu/miku-noodle-stopper-artwork-sketch/'><img width="150" height="150" src="/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Artwork-Sketch-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail" alt="Miku Noodle Stopper Artwork Sketch" loading="lazy" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Artwork-Sketch-150x150.jpg 150w, /wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Miku-Noodle-Stopper-Artwork-Sketch-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" /></a>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Release Details</h2>
<p>As mentioned above, the noodle stopper figure will be released on the 20th of September 2019, but please bear in mind that this is a prize figure; so it will initially only be available at amusement facilities in Japan.</p>
<p>You can find a list of locations where the figure will be available <a href="https://charahiroba.com/prize/shop/item/?id=6851" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</p>
<p>We do recommend keeping an eye on online retailers who specialize in Japanese products, such as <a href="https://www.amiami.com/eng/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AmiAmi</a> and <a href="https://order.mandarake.co.jp/order/?lang=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mandarake</a>, as they may put the figure up for sale at a later date.</p>
<p>So far, I have found <a href="https://www.ninoma.com/index.php/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ninoma</a> and <a href="https://figuya.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Figuya</a> (in Europe) already have pre-orders open for this figure, though Figuya will not have stock until January.</p>
<p>You can pre-order from Ninoma for $18.51 <a href="https://www.ninoma.com/index.php/vocaloid-hatsune-miku-noodle-stopper-figure-furyu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</p>
<p>You can pre-order from Figuya for â‚¬24.90 <a href="https://figuya.com/en/products/hatsune-miku-noodle-stopper-furyu-second-release" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</p>
<p>We will be sure to update you if we find any further information on where to get this adorable figure.</p>
